      "content": "<p>Colombia won Group K convincingly and head into the knockout stage in strong form. Néstor Lorenzo’s side controlled their matches maturely, beating Uzbekistan and Congo DT, and playing a goalless draw against Portugal on the final matchday. Luis Díaz has been the most prominent figure in attack, James Rodríguez has dictated play in midfield, and right-sided defender Daniel Muñoz, who has made strong forward runs, has already scored two goals. </p><p>Ghana advanced from Group L in third place, primarily thanks to their disciplined defensive play. A goalless draw against England highlighted the strength of <b><i>Carlos Queiroz’</i></b>s defensive structure, but a 2–1 loss to Croatia exposed limitations in their attacking play against high-quality opposition. Antoine Semenyo, who suffered an ankle injury against Croatia, is reportedly expected to be fit for Friday’s match. </p><p>Colombia are a stronger side in almost every position and enter the match as roughly 60 % favourites. The match is expected to revolve around Colombia’s possession, with Ghana sitting in a compact defensive shape and looking for chances on quick counterattacks. If Colombia manage to move Ghana’s defensive line quickly enough, they should be able to create a decisive number of scoring chances. The expected goals total is around 2.40, with Colombia contributing about 1.80 and Ghana about 0.80</p><p>But those are of course only numbers. The Ghanaian coach is a superb defensive wizard, and following his team's play is usually no fun at all. I expect Ghana to be extremely defensive here, and it might lead to a dullest match of them all at this stage.</p><p>Good luck!</p><br/><br/><b>该文章通过有道机器翻译，仅供参考:</b><br/><br/><p>哥伦比亚队令人信服地赢得了K组的冠军，并以强劲的状态进入淘汰赛阶段。纳萨姆·洛伦佐的球队成熟地控制了比赛，击败了乌兹别克斯坦和刚果DT，并在最后一个比赛日与葡萄牙打成了一场0比0的平局。路易斯Díaz在进攻端是最突出的人物，詹姆斯Rodríguez在中场主导比赛，而右路后卫丹尼尔Muñoz在前场有很强的跑动，已经进了两个球。 </p>\n<p>加纳以第三名的成绩从L组出线，这主要得益于他们严谨的防守。与英格兰队的一场0比0的平局凸显了球队的实力<b><i>奎罗兹的</i></b>但在2比1负于克罗地亚的比赛中，他们暴露了在面对高质量对手时进攻的局限性。据报道，在对阵克罗地亚的比赛中脚踝受伤的塞门约有望在周五的比赛中复出。 </p>\n<p>哥伦比亚队几乎在每个位置上都更强大，并且以大约60%的热门率进入比赛。本场比赛将围绕哥伦比亚队的控球权展开，加纳队将采取紧凑的防守阵型，寻找快速反击的机会。如果哥伦比亚能够足够快地移动加纳的防线，他们应该能够创造出决定性的得分机会。预计进球总数约为2.40个，其中哥伦比亚约为1.80个，加纳约为0.80个</p>\n<p>但这些当然只是数字。这位加纳教练是一位出色的防守奇才，跟随他的球队踢球通常一点也不好玩。我预计加纳在这里会非常防守，这可能会导致一场在这个阶段最沉闷的比赛。</p>\n<p>好运！</p>",
